{
  "stem": "10588.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- you know, I survived against all possible odds, because in Hitler's totalitarian state, mass murder of the Jews was legal, but to save a Jewish child from Nazi destruction was illegal and punishable by death.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything that we did was illegal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To worship God was illegal, but to burn the-- the Jewish synagogue, that was-- that was legal.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it was a reversal of our commandments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- you know, the Nazis did everything in their power to dehumanize and to destroy me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this is the reason why when they called me number 25673 that I said, I'm not a number.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And today when somebody asks me about number, you know what I tell them?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is my badge of honor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I remember, I was interviewed in a-- on television.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they asked me, could I show the number?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you would have asked me a minute before if I'm going to say something about the number, I probably wouldn't be able to tell you, because I'm pretty much spontaneous person, but I don't do recklessly.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So-- but when I showed the number, I said, why?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Just a number?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Am I just a number?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I pointed to it, and I said, this is my badge of honor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And a reporter from the called into the station.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He wanted to know, why did I call it my badge of honor?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I told him that my family taught me that who I am, my [NON-ENGLISH], my humaneness, does not depend on others-- how others treat me, but how I treat others.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have not killed anybody in my life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have not come committed a crime, yet I have been-- everything that I loved was taken from me and destroyed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So why should I be ashamed?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
